title: LF Duo Partner/s G5+
body:
Hey all,

Plat last season, long story short work got in the way for most of the season so far but im back now. G5 looking to climb.

ADC main but I can play top/jg effective enough in gold.

Games not as fun without atleast a duo. 

Must have a mic and be over 18.

Add me in game: Desire

Cheers.

replies.body: Interested. Jg/Supp main. Can play every support - all champions owned. Currently S2, Been playing mid-tier Gold elo all season. Can comfortably handle Gold elo.
